menu.desc: For selecting via a gauge's time series identifier.

errors.desc: Sets of root mean square errors, and percentage error distributions.

predictions.desc: Includes the original observation, prediction estimates, and error percentages.  For example, lower_q: lower quartile, upper_q: upper quartile, lower_w: lower whisker, upper_w: upper whisker, p_error: percentage error, p_e_lower_w: percentage error lower whisker, p_e_upper_w: percentage error upper whisker .
